Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.40,0:01:25.24,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20}美国 联合国议会厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.76,0:01:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,针对「天人」接连不断极其恶劣的恐怖行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,UNION 人类革新联盟 AEU将缔结军事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.17,0:01:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此宣布 我们将在联合国的管理下 展开打击「天人」的军事行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.37,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三个阵营宣布在联合国的管理下缔结军事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.51,0:01:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由此将诞生史上最大规模的联合国军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.65,0:01:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来事态正随着「天人」的预想发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.84,0:02:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近过激的武力介入行为 是为了统合联合国军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种想法比较妥当吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.72,0:02:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将世界合而为一 那就是「天人」的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.87,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以暴制暴 赢得和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.04,0:02:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说这就是你所追求的世界吗 刹那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.27,0:02:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,计划的第一阶段总算完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想不通为何Trinity的行动成了导火索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样说不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.94,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Trinity对各国的军事基地造成了巨大损害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.52,0:02:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种情况下 就算统合全军 也没有结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会招致舆论的失望和反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有什么内幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说实话 我感到有些不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.71,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Veda的情报没有显示Trinity的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.55,0:03:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及Veda的数据被篡改的事实 让我莫名地感到不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皇·李·诺列嘉发来的密信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「Meister连同机体一起返回普特莱玛奥斯」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK 开作战会议了 回天上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我们该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先观察联合国军的动向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是你 应该已经预测到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为此有些事得先准备好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊安先生 麻烦你带上拉塞 去领取GN Arms好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要使用GN Arms了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姑且只有一架而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的成员开始回收上天的Gundam
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.22,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于要投入GN Arms了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说明情况有够紧迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.52,0:04:07.87,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20}UNION 美国 伊利诺斯基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.89,0:04:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片桐 关于从新型Gundam那夺取的光束刀调查结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 现在顾不上这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.88,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来「天人」里出现了叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.08,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且作为见面礼 还提供了和Gundam同类型的引擎以及搭载了该引擎的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然还有30架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才能做出那种宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.44,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所提供机体的驾驶员 应该会从Over Flags的队员中选择吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然 队长是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,断然拒绝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用Flag打倒Gundam
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在哈瓦德·梅森的墓前立下了誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是队长 Flag的性能无法与Gundam…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,君子一言 驷马难追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.62,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}人革联 俄罗斯南部 军事基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是 Gundam的主引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,资料上说 正式名称为GN Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GN Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.14,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们人革联分配到的GN Drive有10台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机师的人选由你负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.55,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校 请让我担任新型机的机师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然要让你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说少尉所释放的脑量子波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.34,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够对带翼Gundam的机师产生影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一优势可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会全力以赴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.13,0:06:06.84,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}AEU 法国 基地内士官宿舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机师候补只要挑选AEU所属国的王牌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 要不要选那个男人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特里克·戈拉索瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事 少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想邀请上校共进晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.99,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉 现在世界即将迎来巨大的变革期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对此你没有想法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 让人放心不下的男人呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等着 我去准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:55.75,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}磁悬浮列车公司 会长别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是JNN吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答说不打算有任何回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受欢迎真辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 机体的运输工作似乎很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与报酬相应的工作 我会做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格纳·哈维总裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就单刀直入地说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.34,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能将运输中的一架新型机让给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么无论UNION还是AEU都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.82,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请总裁利用手中的权限把我安置进军中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你原本是所属外籍军团的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名号是盖利·比亚吉少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你的才能我有所耳闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 为什么如此想介入其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欠了人家三笔债
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然也有这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.54,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但以我的感觉 不再需要佣兵的时代即将到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.56,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想去能够战斗的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底知道多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说了这只是感觉而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多关照 总裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 都怪那天什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.99,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,采访落了个空 怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才说总裁正在会客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是JNN的特派员 想打听一点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JNN的记者小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然可以 但我有点赶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不介意的话请上车说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 这太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绢江·库斯洛德小姐是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不错 有像您这么漂亮的记者小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 您想打听什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若说错了请别见怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比亚吉先生刚才 是不是和列车公司的总裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格纳·哈维氏会面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问你们谈了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我经营物流业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了确认物资流通状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来向总裁报告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地向总裁报告？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 是私人使用的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不冒犯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能告诉我那些物资是什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 是GN Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GN…Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是跟磁悬浮列车相关的器材吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是驱动MS的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Gundam的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「天人」所拥有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个库尔吉斯少年士兵当机师的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那架Gundam的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库尔吉斯的…少年士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诱拐后洗脑 使其接受战斗训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.76,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,培养成游击队士兵的 不瞒您说 就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你 你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠打仗吃饭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢打仗喜欢得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵循人类原始冲动而活 差劲透顶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐又出差了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烦人的老鼠已经清理掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.28,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是能获得舆论支持的正面宣传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 吃不饱的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路易丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸…爸爸  沙…沙慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.67,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}UNION 高轨道空间站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚里桑德罗大人何必亲自前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你费尽千辛万苦才获得的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让我亲眼见识一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 这也是科纳一族长久以来的夙愿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.99,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚里桑德罗大人 不 科纳家早在三代以前就在谋求介入计划的机会了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要有Veda在 我们就无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时偶然间 一位天使降临在我的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你 利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知遇之恩 无以为报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.08,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是没想到会找到本体的所在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 花了这么长时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利冯兹 你就是我名副其实的天使啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.88,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非洲大陆 西北部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼死拼活给他们干 却突然不来联系 搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别问我 妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不擅长考虑这么复杂的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米迦哥确实是这种类型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.75,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别小看人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好你个哈罗 想被挨千刀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米迦勒 哈罗是Trinity不可或缺的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥 刚才是开玩笑而已 开玩笑的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格纳发来了任务计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内容和平时一样 三天后开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我好等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么 怎么突破保安系统的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.16,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系 总之看到这里就别想活着回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下米迦勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.45,0:14:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位女士我曾在Veda的资料里看到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很荣幸能留在你的记忆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我名叫王留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在为「天人」做特工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位是我的搭档 红龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是个好男人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.34,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能到这里来 说明了你的能力之高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 找我们有何贵干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是来打声招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Trinity小队和我们同属「天人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为特工 我们来协助你们是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可是遭到了你们Gundam的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事有所耳闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.67,0:14:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也并非那边的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说 保持中立立场？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.35,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我归根到底是 支持伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格理念的人之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 王留美 需要时 我们会期待你的援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽力而为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别向他们透露这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向你们保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好吗 大哥 那么快就放他们回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.64,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么大不了的 手头的牌越多越有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个美人儿 是个美人儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别闹别扭 别闹别扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.43,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好吗 大小姐 「天人」正和他们处于敌对状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.04,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无妨 Trinity诱发了世界的变革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您就这么讨厌当今的世界吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.54,0:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 再一成不变的话 我甚至希望它就此毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Exia着舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂时没有变化 Trinity也保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请下令惩罚我们的违令行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.11,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.10,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皇小姐 Trinity有动静了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.07,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲尔德 他们的攻击目标是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们行进方向上的军事基地有 人革联 广州军管区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:51.62,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}人革联 广州方面军屯驻基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,观测班通知全员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.28,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三架疑似新型Gundam的MS 从S9788方向袭来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对本基地发动军事介入行动…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.65,0:17:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次的怨气我忍到现在了
